high_descs: Turn to the right and head to the toilet.
Pick up the left spray bottle from the toilet.
Turn around, turn left and go back to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle in the green trash can.
Look up at the toilet.
Pick up the spray bottle on the toilet.
Turn around completely and go back to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle in the green trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in the trash can.

high_descs: Walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the toilet.
Pick up the leftmost yellow spray bottle off of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk towards the shower, then hang a left and walk forward, turn left again to face the toilet.
Put the yellow spray bottle in the green bin to the left of the toilet.
Take a step forward up to the toilet.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle off of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk towards the shower, then turn around to face the toilet.
Put the yellow spray bottle in the small green bin to the left of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move two yellow spray bottles into a small green bin.

high_descs: Go across room, turn right to face garbage and toilet, proceed to garbage and toilet.
Pick up left spray bottle from back of toilet.
Proceed to garbage can.
Place spray bottle in garbage can, left of toilet.
Look up to face back of toilet.
Pick up spray bottle from back of toilet.
Move left to be in front of garbage can.
Place spray bottle in garbage can with other spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Move spray bottles from back of toilet to garbage can.
